title: Samsung Galaxy S7 Rumored to Start Selling in February 2016
text: With all the fuss surrounding the Galaxy Note5 having died down now that the phone has been launched, Samsung enthusiasts are focusing their attention as well as hopes and dreams on the upcoming Galaxy S7 flagship. Traditionally, Samsung has launched its new Galaxy S phones during the Mobile World Congress, which takes place in Barcelona in late February or early March of each year.
